      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level for MRL 3.",
      "rationale": "Order-of-accuracy tests were performed using manufactured solutions for the incompressible Navier-Stokes equations. Observed convergence rates are consistent with the theoretical second-order spatial accuracy of the finite-volume discretization. No anomalies identified."
